snippet.title: Dr. Emoji - Gameplay video
snippet.description:
Download the game for free: 
Itchio: https://vainary.itch.io/dr-emoji
Global Game Jam: https://globalgamejam.org/2020/games/dr-emoji-0

When you're overwhelmed with emojis, Dr. Emoji is here to help! Six patients come to pour their hearts out, and the good therapist will give them their wise counsel. Or not. It's up to you to interpret what is the issue and how to best help them repair themselves. Interpret the emojis, give your best guess and get the thumbs-up as a reward!
